      <title>津巴布韦请美国帮助提醒银行制裁已放松</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/zimbabwe-enlists-us-to-help-remind-banks-that-sanctions-eased</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦要求美国提醒银行，华盛顿最近放松了对这个南部非洲国家的部分制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/zimbabwe-enlists-us-to-help-remind-banks-that-sanctions-eased</guid>
