    <item>
      <title>亚美尼亚将在与阿塞拜疆的重大协议中割让边境领土</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/armenia-to-cede-border-territory-in-major-deal-with-azerbaijan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚美尼亚同意从 20 世纪 90 年代初以来控制的几个阿塞拜疆边境村庄撤军，这是避免两个邻国重新爆发敌对行动并达成长期难以达成的和平协议的重要一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/armenia-to-cede-border-territory-in-major-deal-with-azerbaijan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 15:59:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国在内塔尼亚胡与贝尔博克发生争执后提出投诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/germany-lodges-complaint-after-report-of-netanyahu-baerbock-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在以色列总理和德国外长安娜莱娜·贝尔博克在特拉维夫举行的一次会议上发生冲突的细节被媒体公布后，德国驻以色列大使向本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的办公室提出了投诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/germany-lodges-complaint-after-report-of-netanyahu-baerbock-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 15:44:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乍得要求美军停止在战略陆军基地的行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/chad-asks-us-troops-to-cease-operations-at-strategic-army-base</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社看到的乍得空军参谋长的一封信显示，乍得呼吁美国从中非国家的一个军事基地撤军，该基地是西方为数不多的打击该地区激烈圣战叛乱的前哨基地之一。 。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/chad-asks-us-troops-to-cease-operations-at-strategic-army-base</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 15:16:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院在民主党的帮助下推进乌克兰援助和 TikTok 禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/house-advances-ukraine-aid-tik-tok-ban-with-democrats-help</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院推进了一项长期搁置的针对乌克兰、以色列和台湾的 950 亿美元援助计划，这一突破标志着乌克兰和美国在欧洲盟友日益痛苦的等待结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/house-advances-ukraine-aid-tik-tok-ban-with-democrats-help</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 15:07:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉丁美洲的低利率梦想破灭，政治困境加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/latin-america-sees-low-rate-dreams-crumble-political-woes-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[引领世界进入充满希望的降息周期的地区警告称，美联储自身货币宽松政策的延迟对其经济复苏构成威胁，并可能加剧国内政治问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/latin-america-sees-low-rate-dreams-crumble-political-woes-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 14:45:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克罗地亚最高法院禁止总统米拉诺维奇担任总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/croat-top-court-bars-president-milanovic-from-becoming-premier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克罗地亚最高法院禁止总统佐兰·米拉诺维奇成为该国下一任总理，称他违反了宪法禁止现任国家元首在议会选举期间参与政治的规定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/croat-top-court-bars-president-milanovic-from-becoming-premier</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:57:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>立陶宛称两名因海军盟友袭击而在波兰被拘留</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/lithuania-says-two-detained-in-poland-over-navalny-ally-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[立陶宛表示，两名波兰公民因上个月在波罗的海国家首都袭击已故俄罗斯反对派领导人阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼的盟友而被拘留。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/lithuania-says-two-detained-in-poland-over-navalny-ally-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 09:23:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称俄罗斯发动致命袭击，轰炸机被击落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/ukraine-says-eight-killed-in-missile-attack-on-central-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰表示，自克里姆林宫入侵以来，乌克兰首次在战斗中击落一架俄罗斯战略轰炸机，此前这架飞机发射了导弹袭击，导致第聂伯罗中部地区至少七人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/ukraine-says-eight-killed-in-missile-attack-on-central-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 06:54:05 GMT</pubDate>
